The natives of [[Kintan/Legends|Kintan]] called the [[Magma/Legends|lava]] rivers in the [[Wannschok|Endless Wastes]] '''Rivers of Fire'''. Like most lava, these rivers reached temperatures around 1300°F to 2200°F, which heated up the air around it also. The black and hard soil around the river formed out of rock and glass.

In [[30 BBY/Legends|30 BBY]], the [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Quinlan Vos/Legends|Quinlan Vos]] and [[Aayla Secura/Legends|Aayla Secura]] crossed a River of Fire on Kintan followed by [[Bok]].

